Items.mt: The sixth one is not to be passed on by those who are vulgar to the bones; the seventh one is not to be passed on by those who are slick in the marketplace; the eighth one is not to be passed on by those who are soft and blunt; the ninth one is not to be passed on by those who are flowery in boxing and kicking; the tenth one is not to be passed on by those who do not know how to cherish.
